la ngươ i vư a bi n na y chơ đơ i nư a tiê ng đê n pha t bư c đư ng đi vê ngô i nhi n n nhân_viên đi đi xuô ng mu a may cuô ng ca m thâ y co nhă c nhơ va thă c mă c vê phâ n thư c cu a mi nh thi ne t mă t n vâ n ti nh ruô i phu t ngô i n li tra đa vô n go i phâ n mơ i xuâ t hiê n chu ng xuô ng đê n thi pha t hiê n bê p ngươ i ta mơ i bă t đâ u la m thư c ma chu ng đa yêu câ u mô t biê t la chu n li đư ng lô i va gă ng đê moi tiê n cu a kha ch bă ng đươ c na y o đê go i la i đem vê chu ng câ n mua thư c vê ma pha i chơ đơ i nư a tiê ng nhi n thâ y_như ng ngươ i đê n cu ng lu c va đê n đa xong rô i vê chu ng câ n mua thư c vê vơ i gia ca ngang bă ng đươ c phu c vu ta i n na y co n o chu ng ră ng phu t se co hiê u na y co y thư c đươ c sư lô bi ch va nha m nhi vươ t sư c chi u đư ng sô phu t ma â y no i le lâ y đô ng hô đê bâ m giơ nha bê p cu a n co lâ p đươ c ki lu c mơ i hai phâ n maki va mô t phâ n hâ p co thê hoa n tha nh ti ch tă c â y cu ng rô i ri t lô i chă ng muô n bă t lô i gi chu ng đươ c tiê n chu ng tra pha i la chu cu a n xe t câ n thâ n la i doanh_thu đê ngâ m coi đa đươ c đê n mư c câ n kha ch nư a chu ng kho i cư a co n thâ y mô t nhân_viên na o nư a ma ngươ c la i vo ng tư n tiê ng nhân_viên ho i vâ y phâ n na y co la m tiê p lơ i lô i thâ t mô t thư phâ n son kha ch ha ng kho i sươ ng mă t ca m gia c chưng hư ng va tuô t hư ng phanh đươ c nê u n na y đa coi kha ch ha ng la thươ ng đê thi pha i bi la nh thư c viê c phu c vu thi pha i thê y sai t chu ng tra ch nê u nha ha ng hê t thư c hê t gas quên yêu câ u t mo n n la tha i đô muô n phu c vu thi chu ng câ n tơ i nư a ca m ơn vê i ho c

location far from the main highway and takes a bit of twisting turning to get to but no narrow alleys decoration gives a korean atmosphere with privacy from the outside the interior has a few places to eat but can be cramped if busy though this place isn t the busiest quality food has korean essence but not real korean food some factors make it off key i think it s mediocre and ok if you aren t looking for anything delicious price adequate for normal meals not mine service today could definitely be a lot better it started with the waitress who got the order wrong i ordered first bibimbap then my husband ordered his meal and there was a second pause between because i gave my menu to him he ordered he wanted rice but the pic he pointed to was soup then he changed his order to rice properly this time he did say no soup in vietnamese i know at least that much vietnamese the waitress took our order then went into the kitchen when the food came there was his tonkatsu rice and soup i asked where my food was and she didn t understand my husband ordered it was entirely in vietnamese she even confirmed the order with us i got angry since she only said sorry and wanted me to eat the soup and ignore my request for the bibimbap she ran back in the kitchen and later there was the bibimbap very ugly and unlike the other post on here i felt cheated since i ordered the same dish that had many things missing we then said we don t want the soup but she refused angrily ate the meal then when it came time to pay she offered a discount when i was outside but told my husband the order was written down we were wrong when she came out to say good bye she said i hope you will come again i was really angry at this remark and decided to be extremely truthful the complete opposite of her i could see in her eyes she didn t mean it that annoyed me more i answered i won t be coming again then she said see you again and i replied no thank you and motioned for her to remove a piece of rice on her chin rude to keep up the game of fake kindness don t butter me up with fake compliments to make things worse and blame the customer never coming again and extremely annoyed with this service one more thing when the chili sauce was jammed she said may i help and i never said yes she put loads of chili sauce by removing the cap and previously applied a lot of soy sauce using a spoon drenched in condiments too much sodium intake too unhealthy she eats it like that no wonder her face was large and puffed too much salt i was in shock as i am a practitioner of natural skin health meaning no botox fillers plastic surgery knowing about what not to is important her upstairs is a spa too there s a sign why did she this omg koreans don t eat it like this eww i wonder what was up with her

second time we visited and it did not disappoint located at the end of le_duan opposite the sofitel this neat little cafe offers a nice spacious interior and comfortable seating free wifi friendly staff and of course great drinks this cafe is a bit quieter than the other coffee houses which is good for a more intimate gathering we ordered an ice chocolate without cream and a blueberry smoothie and a green tea tirimisu to munch on the ice chocolate was a winner very chocolate like without the super sugary taste it was an original iced chocolate at its best the blueberry smoothie was very nice not too milky or heavy and served very chilled the green tea tirimisu cake was a bit misleading as the green tea flavour was very pronounced but the tirimisu component was missing it was a nice cake but not what it was said to be all in all fantastic outing at this nice cafe

i couldnt wait to go to a pet cafe this one was a little far from where we live but it was totally worth our drive the place is very clean for having many animals and their coffee is actually one of the best we have wasnt too strong or watery they have quite a few differnt birds you can hold on the first floor along with a few dogs on the second floor they have cat and a bunnies scattered throughout there are hampsters and frogs in cages i would definitly recomend this place if you like pets and dont have any allergies

i ordered a cheesecake just because i missed having some authentic ones after having failed attempts in other cafes in china and vietnam i liked to seek out the foreign made cafes such as this one with a french taste it was nice and quiet in the cafe with good music and modern decorations the layout was wide and free there were french guests a family beside my table where the manager who is also french kept in conversation with them i was impressed by the manager s presence because he would overlook everything to be quality the waitresses also spoke english which was helpful there were many choices of desserts that looked good but i had already eaten lunch i chose my favorite the_cheesecake yes it may be pricey but when a girl has her cravings a girls gotta eat

la ng cu lâ n địa_danh mới_toanh đà_lạt thứ_ba chi vươ t km đươ ng tư đa la t đi đă c lă c êm a va hai la rư ng thông đe p tuyê t vơ i mơ i biê t viê c to mo đi ta i co la ng cu lâ n đa uô ng phi la ng cu lâ n la mô t điê m tham_quan hoa n toa n mơ i toanh n đô du li ch đa la t chi mơ i va o hoa t đô ng mô t thâ t la mô t điê m du li ch nă m dươ i lu ng sâu ti nh châ t hoang da la ng ma n va đu ng ha ng to a la c đi a giơ i thôn suô i ca n la t h la c dương lâm_đô ng thung lu ng rô ng ha na y co mô t suô i y quanh la nguô n nươ c mô t la ng ngươ i cơ_ho sinh sô ng co go i la dankya bao bo c khoa ng ha đô i rư ng gô m ha rư ng thông va ha rư ng la rô ng viê c đâ u tiên chu ng nghi co le nga y xưa na y co râ t nhiê u cu lâ n va o thơ i điê m đo co n hoang da na y tha nh sinh sô ng cu a cu lâ n ng thu hiê n la nh thâ y ngươ i chi che mă t la i bă ng hai chi trươ c lâ n bi bă t gâ n hê t ca i cu lâ n cu ng co thê bơ i thung lu ng na y cu ng co râ t nhiê u cu lâ n vi ma u thân ma u da cu lâ n mo c nhiê u dươ i ta n rư ng thông va mô i bi y no chuyê n thân tư ma u va ng da bo ma u đen tro chi câ n mưa xuô ng chu ng la i pha t triê n trơ la i la ng cu lâ n xe chu ng cư lươ n đươ ng hai la thông xanh la ng nươ c cu a suô i va ng kê cư thê tơ i thâ y la ng cu lâ n ca m gia c đâ u tiên la co gi vi chi thâ y mô t chiê c ng sơ sa i mô t i đâ t trô ng vơ i nhiê u loa i xe đâ u giô ng mô t i giư xe mô t ga i giư ng kiêm soa t ve kiêm giư xe n ve đô ng ngươ i biê t giư xe miê n phi o đi đươ ng co chiê c xe ngư a vâ y la nhă m hươ ng mô t chiê c xe ngư a gô đê bươ c xuô ng ha ng trăm bâ c thang tâ m mă t â y mơ i ca m nhâ n vê ca i ky vy cu a la ng cu lâ n nê u ca c khu du li ch kha c đa la t tâ n du ng ng tha m hoa la m không_gian la ng ma n thi ng ngươ i la m du li ch ta o kha ch mô t sư thi ch thu đươ c vươ t va chinh_phu c sư gian kho ca m nhâ n sư hoang_sơ cu a nu i rư ng ngoa i viê c nê u thi ch kha ch bo nga n đô ng thuê mô t chiê c xe jeep đê cu ng lao xuô ng chô m đoa n đươ ng km quanh khu vư c kha ch se sư du ng đôi chân đê xuô ng lu ng va đô i loa i chu đa o chen co da i chen ca ca c cu lâ n la hoa kim_châm vơ i ma u va ng nha t hê t ca c bâ c thang la hai câ u treo mô i câ u đươ c o vê bơ i sơ i ca p lơ n cư c ky an toa n câ u nhu n chân mô t ca i la câ u đong_đưa ca i đong_đưa â y co mu i co da i thoang thoa ng co tiê ng cu a gio lu a rư ng la m xôn_xao lo ng dô c trơ i xuô ng cuô i dô c ca ngươ i ma t rươ i phi a đâ u la ng ta n thông thă ng vu t dươ i la t nga n hoa va la la ng cu lâ n â n hiê n sương kho i cu a thung lu ng cư thê thi ch thi cư đi muô n dư ng chân thi co ghê gô co xi ch đu gô kha ch ngô i ma ng tâ m mă t nhi n rư ng thông nhi n hô nươ c to mo thư cu lâ n la gi đi tư na y đê n kha c la i leo câ u treo gă n ng đe n măng_sông va tơ i chơ chô m hô m la ng đuô c nă m hô co sân_chơi đê kha ch la i đêm tâ t nhiên la thă p đuô c huyê n a o ng nha da nh kha ch đêm kiê n tru c tây_nguyên thi ch rư ng đêm ke m mo i di ch vu uô ng cư tiê p tu c đi đươ ng c ng suô i ca n hai la cu lâ n nê u thi ch thi thuê chiê c be tư che o hô câu ca hoă c mô t chiê c câ u gô nho dô c trơ i đi nh đô i ma ngă m ca mô t thung lu ng mênh_mông mô t i co rô ng la da tra i đô t lư a tra i đêm thi ch hơ p vơ i ca c n tre co mô t ma ng nươ c gâ n đi nh câ u mưa ma vâ t du ng đê hư ng nươ c la mô t nô i đô ng rô i la i leo xe ngư a da o hoă c va o chơ chô m hô m đê coi buôn n ca i gi mô t di ch vu cu ng đô c đa o ta i la tă m tiên tâ t nhiên la tă m dươ i suô i ca n giư a lau la ch pha i hiê u la vâ n mă c đô che ng chô ki n đa o chư pha i kho a thân hoa n toa n chơ chô m hô m chơ chô m hô m thư c la mô t nha sa n y n ca c vâ t lưu niê m râ t nhiê u mo n ha ng la phiên n tươ ng nha mô vo gu i tra i bâ u khô mo n ha ng n y nhâ t la i chi nh la ca c chu cu lâ n nhô i vi tơ i la ng cu lâ n chă c chă n pha i mua mô t cu lâ n vê la m ky niê m kê t thu c cuô c ha nh tri nh la va o la ng cơ_ho la mô t la ng nho vơ i va i gian nha co ng chiêng xâu bă p khô treo thuyê n đô c mô c che rươ u co thê no i la ng cu lâ n la mô t mô hi nh du li ch tư kha m pha tư tâ n hươ ng không_gian hoang da cu a nu i rư ng n ngươ i chi khe kha ng n chô ta o lô i đi trô ng it all started years ago with a stroll around town to some sight seeing i stumbled into this place after noticing the crowds on my morning walks it s been a wrap eversince places that only have a few options on the menu are a plus because that means the food is always fresh here you can either choose to have or bun_bo_hue as your meal the_pho was very good i ordered the bun_bo_hue to go for lunch later that day fast forward to now and the quality has still remained spectacular the owner always has a smile on his face and you can tell he appreciates his customers which is rare for a place that stays this busy the food here makes me happy and letting everbody know is the purpose for the review
